- Fix all issues on expect/should interfaces that were causing implementation frames to leak through. Also improve the internal Chai error test helper to validate stack traces. _(Issues: #878, #904, PRs: #922)_
- This fixes custom messages not always being respected. _(Issues: #922, #947, #904, PRs: #916, #923)_
